---
title: Cheesy Beef, Venison & Bacon Lasagne with Radish Salad
description: Layers of ooey-gooey 'béchamel' sauce and beef, venison and bacon are filled to the brim in this one-dish wonder! Topped with
Cheddar cheese and served with a crispy radish salad, this is a pub classic, turned hearty home cooking at its finest!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-beef-venison-bacon-lasagne-76d45856.jpg
